        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2059632906" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7050802321607583886">A book like absolutely no other, Absolutely no other. Never there was and never there will ever be anyone like Angela Y. Davis. My personal hero, and everything I ever want to be. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


