<span id="freeTextContainer2215360904157571133">A brilliant analysis of the women&apos;s movement, beginning with its inception within the abolitionist movement, <i>Women, Race &amp; Class</i> is a must read for anyone wanting to learn more about feminism and racism-within-the-feminist movement.</span>
  <span id="freeText2215360904157571133" style="display:none">A brilliant analysis of the women's movement, beginning with its inception within the abolitionist movement, <i>Women, Race &amp; Class</i> is a must read for anyone wanting to learn more about feminism and racism-within-the-feminist movement.</span>
