      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/1109584-women-race-class">Trivia About Women, Race &amp; Class</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
